quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,32,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Ewe Ibilisi, obele orie ulabeele halala nende abarerere hasi obweni (abasujude)?”"
  15,33,"Naboola mbu; “Shenyala okhurerera hasi obweni omundu wawaloonga khuliloba eliumu, liwumukhanga (nilituywa), elirula khu matoyi amamali akakalukhana ifwani tawe.”"
  15,34,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Mana kharula omo! Toto olondelwe muno."
  15,35,"Ne toto oli nende eshilamo shianje okhula Inyanga yeyindukho.”"
  15,36,"Naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbelesia obwiyangu okhula inyanga yabalilamusibwa.”"
  15,37,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Toto ewe oli mubalia bahesibwe obwiyangu."
  15,38,"Okhula inyanga yebise bimanyishe biarebwaho.”"
  15,39,"Naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, shingala wukholele okhukora, toto nditsa okhubaronela (abandu) khushialo, ne toto nditsa okhubakosia boosi."
  15,40,"Halali abasumba bobo mubo abawulwa.”"
  15,41,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Ino ni injila yokhwitsa ewanje ingololofu."
  15,42,"Ne toto ewe sholaba nende obunyali khu abasumba banje tawe, halali balia abakhulondakhwo mubalia abakora ."
  15,43,"Ne toto Jahannam niho habundu wabu wabakasilibwa boosi."
  15,44,"Ili nende emiliango saba, ne buli omuliango kuli nende ebuleka yakwakabulilwa mubo.""
  15,45,"Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mumikunda chiomwikulu nende tsisebele."
  15,46,"Injilemwo mushironyo, nomulembe."
  15,47,"Ne khulirusia amakhonye akali mubilifu biabu, ne baliba (shinga) abananda nibekhale khubisala biobwami nibahengana."
  15,48,"Shibulibatilakhwo obuchong’e bwosibwosi omo tawe, ne shibalirusibwamwo tawe."
  15,49,"Boolela abasumba banje mbu toto esie nesie Owobulesheli obunji, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  15,50,"Ne mbu toto eshinyasio shianje nisho eshinyasio eshilulu muno."
  15,51,"Ne baboolele amakhuwa kabacheni ba Ibrahim."